## Post Structure

Each post follows this structure:

```
TITLE: An assertion, not a topic
  ✓ "Proof of Work Beats Promises"
  ✗ "About Documentation"

HOOK (1-2 sentences)
  - Provocative claim, challenge, or question
  - Grabs attention immediately

---
<img src="/images/..." alt="..."/>

STAKES (1 paragraph)
  - Why this matters
  - What's at risk if ignored
  - What's possible if applied

CORE PRINCIPLE (1-3 paragraphs)
  - The thesis stated clearly
  - Systems vs Goals framing where applicable
  - Bold the mantra

CONCRETE EXAMPLE (1-2 paragraphs)
  - Real scenario, not hypothetical
  - Before/after or good/bad contrast

CLOSE (1-2 sentences)
  - Restate the principle
  - Or: Call to action
  - Or: The post title repeated as a punch
```

**Target length:** 400-1200 words. Never overstays.

