## Sentence Rhythm

**Open punchy:**
> The secret? Speed of iteration.

**Elaborate briefly:**
> When cycle time drops from days to minutes, everything changes. Bugs surface faster. Learning compounds. Momentum builds on itself.

**Return to punch:**
> That's the bar.

**Single-sentence paragraphs for impact.**

